         MACRO
         FILEDSCT
FILEDSCT DSECT                    DEFINES A FILE DESCRIPTION TABLE
FILETBEG EQU   *
FILEDDNM DS    CL8                DD NAME
FILE@DCB DS    F                  ADDRESS OF DCB FOR FILE
FILE@IB  DS    F                  ADDRESS OF INPUT BUFFER STRING
FILE@OB  DS    F                  ADDRESS OF OUTPUT BUFFER STRING
FILE@RD  DS    F                  ADDRESS OF READ ROUTINE FOR FILE
FILE@WR  DS    F                  ADDRESS OF WRITE ROUTINE FOR FILE
FILERDCT DS    F
FILEWRCT DS    F
FILECHOD DS    F                  BIT MAP OF OUTPUT FILES TO ECHO TO
FILEIBML DS    H                  MAXIMUM LENGTH OF INPUT STRING
FILEOBML DS    H                  MAXIMUM LENGTH OF OUTPUT STRING
FILECCHR DS    X                  CONTROL CHARACTER FOR FILE (IF USED)
FILEFLAG DS    X                  FLAG BYTE
         CNOP  0,8
FILETEND EQU   *
FILETLEN EQU   FILETEND-FILETBEG
STDIPT   EQU   1
STDOPT   EQU   2
HRDOPT   EQU   4
FILEALOC EQU   X'80'              DD CARD IN TIOT
FILEOPEN EQU   X'40'              FILE IS OPEN
FILEUSE  EQU   X'20'              FILE MAY BE USED
FILEIPT  EQU   X'10'              FILE MAY BE READ FROM
FILEOPT  EQU   X'08'              FILE MAY BE WRITTEN TO
FILEERR  EQU   X'04'              FILE HAS AN ERROR
FILECNTL EQU   X'02'              FILE HAS CONTROL CHARACTER ON OUTPUT
         MEND
